node.text:
Three new sapphire case versions of the @jacobandco x @bugatti Twin Turbo Furious 👀

A horological machine packed with complications such as double triple-axis sequential high-speed tourbillons, monopush chronograph, minute repeater and a power reserve indicator 👌🏼

It is the first watch in the history of haute horlogerie to place a decimal minute repeater inside a fully sapphire crystal case, which took approximately 15 months to design and produce.

node.text:
Behind the scenes of crafting the @jacobandco Opera Godfather 💎

The Opera Godfather comes in a 49mm rose gold or black ceramic and domed sapphire crystal case, the large size allowing for the placement of two barrels hand-set with 666 brilliant white diamonds (approx. 1.85 cts) specially crafted to reproduce the music.

The triple axis tourbillon dances it’s round-the-clock mechanical ballet.
Limited edition of 88 pieces  and priced at $420,000 💸
